Tracey's Mon-
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Library: Fan Fiction, Poetry, Birthday List, Links & Non-Fiction Archive: Filk Songs: Tracey's Mon-
By Icelord13 on Tuesday, March 23, 2004 - 06:49 pm:

After listening to the Stacey's Mom song over and over again, I've decided to do a parody. It's basically one of those things where a human likes a pixie (like in torey's story) and it's a spoof on the whole thing with the mom. I added color just because I needed something to do after this was done. blue means its the lead singer and red means its just some guy in the background. Ah well, enjoy.

"Stacey's Mom" is ©Fountains of Wayne

Tracey's Mon-

Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on
Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on
Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on
Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on

Tracey, you got a new monster, can I see?
Can I see?
We can hang around, by the spirit tree
Hang by the tree
Is your monster back, from her errantry?
Errantry
Is she there, or will I wait for eternity?
Eternity

You know I’m not the little boy that I used to be
I’m all grown up now, baby can’t you see?

Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on.
She’s all I want, and I’ve waited for so long.
Tracey can’t you see, you’re just not the rancher for me.
I know it might be wrong but, I’m in love Tracey’s mon-

i{Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on
Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on}

Tracey do you remember when I fed your mon-
i{Feed your mon-
Pixie came out, just her undergarments on
i{Garments on}
I could tell she liked me from the way she would stare
i{Way she would stare}
And the way she said, “I’d like the meat over there.”
i{Meat over there}

And I know that you think it’s just a fantasy
But since Pixie came out
She’d need a rancher just like me

Tracey’s mon…ster’s got it goin on
She’s all I want, and I’ve waited for so long.
Tracey can’t you see, you’re just not the rancher for me.
I know it might be wrong but, I’m in love with Tracey’s mon-

Hope you liked it! -Icelord13
